{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-types-page-js","path":"/services/chauffeur-services/","result":{"data":{"page":{"title":"Chauffeur Services","content":"\n<p>Volta4u manages a significant fleet of vehicles for the Chauffeur Service operations</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The experienced drivers of our company serve senior executives, multinational companies, EU government departments in Greece and abroad.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Given the need to move to a larger target market, our fleet is expanding to include Premium Sedan cars &nbsp;such as the Mercedes S-Class, the BMW 7 Series, exclusive SUVs such as the Range Rover Sport Vehicles, the Porsche Cayenne S.<br>In addition to the above categories, our fleet includes Mini Van cars such as Mercedes Vito, Minibuses and executive coaches.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the services provided are also<br>transfer from / to the airport to / from the desired location upon notification by the customer as well as from the airport upon arrival of a private flight.<br>&#8211; the provision of chauffeur service with luxury vehicles for social events of weddings, receptions, conferences, etc.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Contact us at <strong>+2109735000</strong> or send e-mail to <strong><a href=\"mailto:reservsations@volta4u.com\">reservsations@volta4u.com</a></strong> and let us guarantee the maximum reliability, with consistency of confidential and discreet service.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, pre-book your chauffeured trip and let us guarantee maximum reliability &amp; trustworthy service.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Additional information about Chauffeur Services:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>All drivers speak fluent Greek and English.</li><li>All drivers are fully registered in accordance with Greek laws and regulations</li><li>All our vehicles are highly comfortable and air-conditioned</li><li>All vehicles are registered and certified as required by law</li><li>First-class absolutely confidential service</li><li>Vehicles without badges and with protected privacy</li></ul>\n","databaseId":487